707206f-a.title: Brooklyn: Vernon Ave. - Tompkins Ave.
707206f-a.text:
Vornon Avenue, east from Tompkins Avenue, showing
a W. P. A. sower projoct.

707205f-a.title: Brooklyn: Vernon Ave. - Tompkins Ave.
707205f-a.text:
Vernon Avenue, wast from and across Tompkins Avenue,
showing a W. P. A. sewer project. On the left, At the
S. E. cornor of tho two avenues, is tho Brooklyn Traffic
Court.
